Classes
Class
Description
Course
This class represent a course in the wolfScheduler.
CourseRecordIO
This class is responsible to read and write course records from and to the text files, it can read a file that have the course informations, and create course object from each valid line, it also ignores any invalid or duplicated courses.
WolfScheduler
This class is responsible to manage the course catalog and the student schedule, it allows the student to add and remove courses, also it allows the student to export the schedule.
WolfSchedulerGUI
GUI for the WolfScheduler project.
